Inez Clough https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inez_Clough 0 Inez Clough was a prominent African American singer, dancer, and film actress in the early 1900s. Clough was born on March 1, 1873 in Worcester, Massachusetts and died on November 21, 1933 in Elgin, Illinois.
